tafsir[20]{c,v,t}:
  90,1,"Alla woondirii e leydi kormaandi ndi ndiin woni Makka."
  90,2,"E Aan- nelaaɗo-na dagani Ma ko mbaɗɗa e ndii leydi, hono warde potɗo wareede, e dahde potɗo daheede."
  90,3,"Alla woondiri baaba mum aade en, o woondiri kadi ko yalti e ɓiɓɓe mum."
  90,4,"Ko goongo Min tagii aade e tampere, o hawra e tamperaaji aduna."
  90,5,"Mbela aade sikku si o waɗii goopi hay gooto waawah e mum hay huunde, hay si ko Alla tagɗo mbo o."
  90,6,"O wiya: Mi nafkii jawdi keewndi pawandirndi."
  90,7,"Mbela o basorotooɗo ko o tottiri ko Alla yi*aani mbo? te alah kaasboowo mbo, holto o dañi kaake mum ɗe."
  90,8,"Mbela Min mbaɗanaani mbo gite ɗe o yiirata."
  90,9,"E ɗemngal e toni ɗiɗi hombo yeewtira mum."
  90,10,"Min nganndini mbo laawol jam e laawol meere."
  90,11,"Ko o ɗaɓɓiraaɗo falgude palal keetngal mbo e aljanna o taƴa ngal o yawta ngal."
  90,12,"Hol ko anndi Ma-aan nelaaɗo-palal ngal o foti taaɓaade ngam o naata aljanna."
  90,13,"Ngaal palal woni rimɗinde daande gorko maa debbo."
  90,14,"Nde o ñamminta e ñalngu ngu newaaki heɓde ñaamde."
  90,15,"Suka yatiime baaba, jiidaaɗo ko ɓadi."
  90,16,"Wollo baasɗo mbo alah hay ndiga."
  90,17,"Refti o laati e ɓeen goonɗiɓe Alla, yogo e mum en wasiyii yogo muñal e ɗoftaade e goopi e musibbaaji, ɓe mbasandiri yurmondirde."
  90,18,"Ko ɓeen sifariiɓe ɗiin sifaaji ngoni joman en ñaaame."
  90,19,"ɓeen yedduɓe aayeeje Amen tellinaaɗe e nelaaɓe Amen, ɓeen ngoni joman nane."
  90,20,"Ina e dow mum en yiite uddaange ñande darnga ɓe lepte e henge."
